stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> World
    World --> World: World command / tick
    World --> Battle: Encounter
    Battle --> Battle: Action / playback
    Battle --> World: Finished

    note right of World
      Owns WorldApplication
      Refreshes WorldObservation
    end note

    note right of Battle
      Owns GameBattleSession
      Rejects unavailable actions
    end note
